First-ever, fully-secured mobile data vault! Secure, save, and easily manage personal & business sensitive mobile data with POMM patented, electronic mobile-phone case
















First-ever, fully-secured mobile data vault! Secure, save, and easily manage personal & business sensitive mobile data with POMM patented, electronic mobile-phone caseBiometric authenticationPOMM multi-layered security approach allows access only to its authorized owner via biometric face/palm/in-air gesture authentication capabilitiesPhysiological  protectionPOMM integrated physiological protection sensors monitor access to POMM secure content, blocking access once signs of stress are detected on user’s side Isolated systemPOMM is a secure, isolated and encrypted data depository totally sealed from the Internet/Public Cloud, available 24/7 regardless of Internet or mobile connectivity Secure storage/communicationTo complete POMM's multi-layered security, all stored data and communication is encrypted with cutting-edge hardware technologies and software algorithms 


Download Specsheet

POMM Concept Our natural right for the privacy and security of our mobile data!With hacking and ransomware mobile threats on the rise, POMM moves in to protect mobile data security and privacy.
Soon to be Available on for early-bird online purchase!
POMM – standing for Privacy-on-my-Mind – offers private and business users the highest level of mobile data security; by upgrading Android mobile phones with multistep biometric authentication, physiological protection from coercion, encrypted communication, vast isolated storage and secured applications.
POMM smart electronic add-on case keeps intact all the operational capabilities of the commercial smartphone it is attached to; at the same time adding a secure smart mobile device to store and manage data.
READ MORE ABOUT OUR STORY
MY POMMElectronic case add-on to my personal smartphoneMY POMMTM allows only authorized users quick access 24/7 anywhere to its protected highly isolated large additional data storage area, with no need to access Internet or external clouds.
MY POMMTM integrated biometric & physiological sensors authenticate legitimate user/s, sense physiological/emotional stress and ensure utmost privacy, security and safety of use of the selected sensitive personal and work-related/corporate data.

All day power with POMM TM integrated battery
Secured Apps, no Internet/Public Cloud exposure
Up to 256 GB secured storage

thousands of documents & emails
32,000+ photos
20+ hours of video
18,000 + songs


Secured gallery, contacts, messaging, browsing
Secured passwords safe

POMM secure end-to-end solutions for mobile environmentsSMB & Corporate, Healthcare, Fintech, IoT Automotive industry POMM TM enables secured encrypted data exchange and management with authorized corporate and service provider servers.
POMM TM, as part of a secured system, uses its integrated NFC/USB connections to perform updates from servers, cloud services or other POMM devices. This mode of operation requires dedicated POMM TM software drivers and APIs to encrypt the communication and data exchange with third party servers.
POMM TM, as part of a secured system, is the key/e-token for accessing and using end-to-end proprietary security systems in various verticals:

SMB & Corporate
Healthcare
Fintech
IoT Automotive industry




