Technology Hardware, Storage and Peripherals

Company Overview of POMM Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
POMM Inc. develops and commercializes biometrically authenticated and biosensor-protected privacy solutions for smartphones. It offers POMM (Privacy On My Mind) device, a compact, biometrically secured data depository, attached as an add-on to the personal smartphone, and accessible to no one but its owner. The company offers a rechargeable battery protective case with local built-in secured depository, providing storage of various data and files for user, such as pictures and video gallery, camera, contacts, secured dials, notes, calendars, emails, documents, and others. POMM Inc. was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Atlanta, Georgia.


985 Citadel Drive N.E.Suite AAtlanta, GA 30324United StatesFounded in 2010



