 Company information


    POM Incorporated is descended from the first parking meter company -- Magee-Hale Park-O-Meter. POM is a privately owned Arkansas corporation and manufactures its housings and electronic mechanisms in a 67,000 sq. ft. facility in Russellville, Arkansas. POM currently meters over 286,000 parking spaces worldwide, is ISO 9001:2000 certified, and integrates with smartcard, wireless, and ticketwriting technology. A leader in product innovation, POM is best known for its dedication to quality and customer service.
    
    





